{"id":584639,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/05/【图说天朝】北京798园区保安殴打女同/","date":"2018-05-14T06:36:58Z","modified":"2018-05-14T06:47:11Z","title":"【图说天朝】北京798园区保安殴打女同","content":"<p>作者：削美丽</p>\n<p>5月13日，北京798园区保安人员殴打女同性恋，只因她们佩戴彩虹饰品进入园区。网友发布了一张现场照片让我印象深刻，所以画了下来。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/image_uploaded_from_ios_1024-1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-584641\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/image_uploaded_from_ios_1024-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"796\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/image_uploaded_from_ios_1024-1.jpg 578w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/image_uploaded_from_ios_1024-1-170x300.jpg 170w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/殴打女同.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-584640\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/殴打女同.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"643\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/殴打女同.jpg 1280w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/殴打女同-210x300.jpg 210w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/殴打女同-768x1097.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/殴打女同-717x1024.jpg 717w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">今日，在北京798艺术区@票圈君 派放彩虹徽章声援 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/LGBT?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#LGBT</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E6%81%90%E5%90%8C%E6%97%A5?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#国际不再恐同日</a> 参加者发现原定的园区内活动地点停着数辆警车，举办方将地点移至北门进行。由于人数众多，保安将人群驱散开，并表示身戴彩虹徽章的人不可以进入园区，并与两名女性发生了肢体冲突，并动手将其踹倒在地。视频来自@YAWARUKAS <a href=\"https://t.co/zCCCBJx2cK\">pic.twitter.com/zCCCBJx2cK</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; heixiao (@hei_xiao) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hei_xiao/status/995626578276069377?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 13, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,21627],"tags":[34613,27316,34340,34612,34614,9503]}